<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT18">
<l>iḷaippiṉai yiyakkam nīkki yiruntumuṉ ṉimaiyaik kūṭṭi</l>
<l>aḷappilaim pulaṉa ṭakki yaṉpavar kaṇṇē vaittu</l>
<l>tuḷakkamil cintai ceytu tōṉṟaluñ cuṭarviṭ ṭāṅkē</l>
<l>viḷakkiṉai vitiyiṟ kāṇpār meymmaiyē kāṇkiṟ pārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Removing weariness or movement [and] sitting, closing [their] upper eyelids,</l>
<l>Subduing [their] unbounded five senses, fixing [their] love on only him,</l>
<l>Making [their] thoughts not waver, in [this] method, those who see [him],</l>
<l>[As] a lamp as soon as he appears there emitting light, are able to see the truth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
